	<section>
		<h3>Frontier</h3>
		<p>
			The Frontier Development Platform is our foundation for building new products.  To be a successful web developer you must become a practitioner of these technologies.  We have divided the achievement for this skill into the three guild levels, apprentice, journeyman, and master.  Earning the apprentice level means that you have accumulated knowledge regarding these important technologies.  Earning the journeyman level means that you have the knowledge and skill necessary for day-to-day production work. Earning a master level means that you are acting as a mentor and teacher, and have demonstrated an advanced level of understanding thru study and projects.
		</p>
		<h4>You are expected to have a basic understanding of the following concepts:</h4>
		<p>
			NodeJS, Express framework, EJS pages, experiments, Strong i18n, Git, controls, Angular, and PAAS such as Heroku.
		</p>
